    {
      "start": 89.0,
      "end": 89.56,
      "text": "Venture."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.66,
      "end": 89.86,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.98,
      "end": 91.16,
      "text": "Think of venture."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.32,
      "end": 91.98,
      "text": "Something new."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.16,
      "end": 93.18,
      "text": "A new business."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.26,
      "end": 93.54,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.76,
      "end": 94.72,
      "text": "A new hobby."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.96,
      "end": 95.98,
      "text": "A new venture."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.2,
      "end": 96.48,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.6,
      "end": 98.58,
      "text": "So, any new ventures for you recently?"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.94,
      "end": 100.92,
      "text": "Oh, I'm doing this and that."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.06,
      "end": 101.28,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.26,
      "end": 103.18,
      "text": "Next one."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.46,
      "end": 104.74,
      "text": "Keep them away."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.48,
      "end": 109.58,
      "text": "Away가 붙었으니까 뭔가 멀리 떨쳐내는 그런 느낌이 들잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.78,
      "end": 110.42,
      "text": "Keep them away."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.52,
      "end": 111.3,
      "text": "Keep them away."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.36,
      "end": 111.88,
      "text": "They're scary."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.88,
      "end": 114.44,
      "text": "Oh, 그들 무서우니까 그들 멀리해."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.0,
      "end": 115.88,
      "text": "이런 의미잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.96,
      "end": 116.86,
      "text": "It's a common sentence."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.94,
      "end": 117.22,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.22,
      "end": 119.88,
      "text": "Especially in scary scenes, scary movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.04,
      "end": 120.28,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.6,
      "end": 121.6,
      "text": "Keep them away."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.74,
      "end": 124.28,
      "text": "그들을 멀리하다 라는 동사 구문입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.84,
      "end": 125.6,
      "text": "Luxury."
